Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三个人一定\N都要成为Meister-乙HiME喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（毕业照片\N～埃尔斯汀·贺最后的微笑～)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我明明就是脚受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果连这种事都让你帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，接下来帮你洗身体喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪学姊教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪学姊教了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，妮娜也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始服务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱…爱莉卡…不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑嫩嫩～软绵绵～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，好惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张是你的份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前出去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡硬拖着我们去拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就说不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会很宝贝它的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们现在在这里的证据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记的…永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，我得写出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我无可取代的挚友们
